This API provides a Co-simulation between CARLA(Car Learning to Act) AND SUMO (Simulation of Urban Mobility).

requirements:

- Python version >= 3.7
- Carla version >= 0.9.14
- SUMO version >= 1.18.0

Usage

Run CARLA:

- ./CarlaUE4.exe -dx11 -carla-rpc-port=4000

Run API:

- py -3.7 api.py

Here's how to make requests to the API:

Example Request:

curl -X GET http://localhost/startSimulation
curl -X POST -d '{"key1":"value1", "key2":"value2"}' http://localhost/startSimulation

Payload:
{
"radar": True
}
